This repository holds the scripts and config files for the LongView LDM server.

The directory LDM holds the LDM config files and the crontab and incrontab configuration.

The directory bin holds the scripts located in /usr/local/bin

The directory wsi_svc holds the crontab and incrontab configuration for user wsi_svc.

The directory etc holds the files in /longview/etc that control the status for primary/backup as well as the north_america_site.list file.

